    Method new()

    Usage

    mg_Logger$new(
  db_tablestring = NULL,
  log_db = getOption("mg.log_db"),
  log_conn = NULL,
  log_path = getOption("mg.log_path"),
  ts = NULL,
  tic = Sys.time()
)

    Arguments

    log_db

    The specification to where db logs are stored ("schema.table"). If NULL, no db logs are created.

    log_path

    Path to a directory of log files.

    log_path

    The path where logs are stored. If NULL, no file logs are created.
